message.content:
To create a CSV file containing the information you requested about US Presidents, I'll need to gather data from reliable sources. This includes:

1. President's name
2. Age when starting office
3. Year they started office
4. Number of years they served

I won't be able to provide an actual CSV file here due to formatting limitations, but I can certainly give you the data in a structured format that you can easily copy into a CSV editor or spreadsheet program like Microsoft Excel or Google Sheets.

Here's the data:

| President Name | Age When Started Office | Year Started Office | Years Served |
|----------------|-------------------------|---------------------|--------------|
| George Washington| 57                      | 1789                | 2            |
| John Adams       | 61                      | 1797                | 2            |
| Thomas Jefferson | 43                      | 1801                | 4            |
| James Madison    | 57                      | 1809                | 4            |
| James Monroe     | 58                      | 1817                | 2            |
| John Quincy Adams| 61                      | 1825                | 4            |
| Andrew Jackson   | 57                      | 1829                | 3            |
| Martin Van Buren | 56                      | 1837                | 4            |
| William Henry Harrison | 65 | 1841 | 1 |
| John Tyler       | 54                      | 1841                | 2            |
| James Knox Polk  | 59                      | 1845                | 3            |
| Zachary Taylor   | 54                      | 1849                | 1            |
| Millard Fillmore | 57                      | 1850                | 2            |
| Franklin Pierce  | 61                      | 1853                | 4            |
| James Buchanan   | 65                      | 1857                | 4            |
| Abraham Lincoln  | 52                      | 1861                | 4 (assassinated) |
| Andrew Johnson   | 61                      | 1865                | 4 (impeached, resigned) |
| Ulysses S. Grant | 49                      | 1869                | 4            |
| Rutherford B. Hayes | 52 | 1877 | 1 |
| James A. Garfield| 47                      | 1881                | 1 (assassinated) |
| Chester A. Arthur| 48                      | 1881                | 3            |
| Grover Cleveland | 50                      | 1885, 1893          | 2 x 2        |
| Benjamin Harrison| 67                      | 1889                | 4            |
| William McKinley   | 52                      | 1897                | 4 (assassinated) |
| Theodore Roosevelt | 42 | 1901, 1905 | 4 x 2        |
| William Howard Taft| 51                      | 1909                | 2            |
| Woodrow Wilson     | 56                      | 1913                | 4            |
| Warren G. Harding  | 52                      | 1921                | 4 ( scandals) |
| Calvin Coolidge    | 50                      | 1923                | 2            |
| Herbert Hoover     | 57                      | 1929                | 4            |
| Franklin D. Roosevelt | 63 | 1933 | 4 (re-elected) |
| Harry S. Truman    | 60                      | 1945                | 4            |
| Dwight D. Eisenhower | 62 | 1953 | 4            |
| John F. Kennedy    | 47                      | 1961 (assassinated) | 4 (partial) |
| Lyndon B. Johnson  | 50                      | 1963 (assassinated) | 2            |
| Richard Nixon      | 46                      | 1969                | 2 ( resigned )|
| Gerald Ford        | 58                      | 1974                | 1            |
| Jimmy Carter       | 58                      | 1977                | 4            |
| Ronald Reagan      | 60                      | 1981                | 4            |
| George H.W. Bush   | 62                      | 1989                | 4            |
| Bill Clinton       | 46                      | 1993                | 4            |
| George W. Bush     | 57                      | 2001                | 2            |
| Barack Obama       | 47                      | 2009                | 2            |
| Donald Trump       | 46                      | 2017                | 1 ( partial)|
| Joe Biden          | 58                      | 2021                | 2            |

Please note:
- The age when starting office is based on the president's birth date and their inauguration date.
- Some presidents served multiple terms, indicated by "2 x 2" under years served.
- Years in parentheses indicate partial terms due to assassination or resignation.

You can copy this data into your preferred CSV editor or spreadsheet program to create the actual CSV file.
